			<div class="desc">
				<div class="question">What if Pixels are Edible?</div>
						
				<div style="margin-top:20px;">Pixel Monster outfits people with subversive technology for web images which transforms the passive end user into an active web space owner. To send a monster out you click the icon on the top left corner on the image, it will munch pixels and reclaim the web space for you!</div> 
				<div>It introduces the potential of opening up the Web for personal expressions in visual forms other than text through browser extension technology, which is a realization of graffiti on the web. The ability to see the web as public space, where people can comment and shape the landscape is a radical shift towards open digital society.</div>
		
